---
// Testimonio en formato banda cinematic — foto full-bleed con quote overlay
---

<section class="testimonio" id="impacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonio-head">
      <div class="eyebrow center">Historias reales</div>
      <h2>Una visita a un colegio.<br><span class="highlight">Una familia</span> nueva.</h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cinema-wrap">
    <div class="cinema-card">
      <img
        class="cinema-photo"
        src="/assets/photos/gallery/large/foto_44.jpg"
        alt="Grupo de estudiantes con un líder de LUZ Impacto tras un evento en su colegio"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="cinema-overlay"></div>
      <div class="cinema-content">
        <div class="cinema-quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="cinema-quote">
          Esa tarde <span class="cinema-emph">Dios me agarró</span>. No sé cómo explicarlo mejor. Mis amigas y yo lloramos como nunca, y desde ese día somos diferentes. Ya no me siento sola en lo que sentía.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonio {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--on-dark);
    padding: 120px 0 100px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .testimonio::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    left: -100px;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(252,211,77,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .testimonio-head {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 56px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .testimonio-head .eyebrow.center { color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .testimonio-head h2 {
    color: var(--on-dark);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .highlight { color: var(--yellow); font-weight: 600; }

  .cinema-wrap {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .cinema-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .cinema-photo {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 35%;
    display: block;
  }
  .cinema-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 0%,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 55%,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.85) 100%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cinema-content {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    padding: 56px;
    color: white;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .cinema-quote-mark {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 100px;
    line-height: 0.4;
    color: var(--yellow);
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cinema-quote {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3.2vw, 38px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: white;
    max-width: 900px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  .cinema-emph {
    color: var(--yellow);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .testimonio { padding: 80px 0 64px; }
    .cinema-wrap { padding: 0 16px; }
    .cinema-card { aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; border-radius: 20px; }
    .cinema-content { padding: 28px 24px 32px; }
    .cinema-quote-mark { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cinema-overlay {
      background: linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.10) 0%,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 50%,
        rgba(0,0,0,0.92) 100%
      );
    }
  }
</style>
